  "organic": [
    {
      "title": "骑士飞赴底特律!哈登生涯抢七战4胜4负:明日力争率队晋级东决",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_5356a08e34254152",
      "snippet": "<p>北京时间5月17日,骑士官方更新社媒,晒出了全队抵达机场,准备飞往底特律的画面｡明日,骑士将在客场对阵活塞,打响这轮系列赛的抢七大战｡这也是骑士连续第二轮打抢七,在首轮对阵猛龙的系列赛中,他们赢下抢七大战,晋级东部半决赛｡</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.",
      "date": "2026-05-17 05:36:03"
    },
    {
      "title": "奥登:被选中前一分钟我才知道是状元,因为杜兰特真的很出色",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_7766a08a65331552",
      "snippet": "<p>前NBA状元格雷格-奥登近日在播客节目《Ball Up Top》中,回忆了2007年NBA选秀夜的紧张时刻｡</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-2766641710-002F8D0644AF2A0B7F1941BD58C31DFE/0?fmt=jpg&size=95&h=474&w=630&ppv=1' ",
      "date": "2026-05-17 01:16:03"
    },
    {
      "title": "马刺狂胜森林狼,时隔9年重返西决!核心三人组被誉新时代“GDP”",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_0796a08eee840752",
      "snippet": "<p>2026年NBA季后赛西区次轮战局尘埃落定,圣安东尼奥马刺迎来久违的强势复苏｡5月16日,马刺以139:109､狂胜30分的悬殊比分击溃明尼苏达森林狼,系列赛以4:2淘汰对手,成功晋级西区决赛｡这是马刺阔别整整9年再度重返西决舞台,一扫多年重建阴霾｡美媒更是盛赞球队全新核心三人组,称其为马刺新时代的“GDP”组合｡</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.",
      "date": "2026-05-17 06:25:45"
    },
    {
      "title": "进攻端的贡献度太低了!骑士先发小前锋的问题实在是太明显了?",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_3336a08a6ed04752",
      "snippet": "<p>在此前的一场NBA东部半决赛中,背水一战的底特律活塞以115比94战胜了主场作战的克利夫兰骑士｡本场比赛后,活塞顽强地将系列赛总比分扳成了3比3,双方又回到了同一起跑线上｡接下来双方将回到底特律并且通过残酷的抢七大战来决定最终晋级东部决赛的名额｡</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.",
      "date": "2026-05-17 01:18:38"
    },
    {
      "title": "NBA playoffs 2025: Every conference semifinalist's path to the title - ESPN",
      "link": "https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/45026101/nba-playoffs-2025-thunder-celtics-cavs-pacers-knicks-nuggets-warriors-wolves-path-title",
      "snippet": "The NBA's conference semifinals represent an escalation in both stakes and quality of competition. Nobody expected the play-in teams -- outside of the Golden State Warriors -- to compete for the 2025 title. But once the playoff field is whittled to eight remaining contenders, they all have a legitimate chance. Just look at what happened in the opening days of the second round. Road teams upset the higher-seeded No. 1 Cleveland Cavaliers , No. 2 Boston Celtics and No. 1 Oklahoma City Thunder ing team -- sorted in order of title odds by ESPN's Basketball Power Index (BPI) -- can win the 2025 NBA championship. Jump to a team: BPI odds: To reach conference finals: 63.0% To reach NBA Finals: 51.5% To win 2025 title: 39.9% Statistical models consider the Thunder to be overwhelming title favorites. And why wouldn't they be? Oklahoma City set an NBA record for point differential (plus-12.9 per game), is led by likely MVP Shai Gilgeous-Alexander and boasts one of the best defenses in NBA histor",
      "date": "2025-05-07 15:31:00"
    },
    {
      "title": "NBA Playoffs predictions & picks for every game of 2026",
      "link": "https://www.dimers.com/bet-hub/nba/schedule",
      "snippet": "Your data-driven hub for NBA predictions today NBA betting advice feels like guessing some nights, doesn’t it? There’s no shortage of opinions or gut feelings, but it’s all just adding to the noise. Dimers provides clarity and cuts through that chaos with data-driven NBA predictions you can trust. We use advanced data modeling to forecast moneyline , point spreads , and total points ( over/under ) for every NBA matchup. Our predictions give you the insight to approach every contest with confidence—from classic rivalries like the Boston Celtics vs. Los Angeles Lakers to recent champion showdowns like the Denver Nuggets vs. Oklahoma City Thunder. Think of us as your NBA betting command center: probabilities, value bets, and top odds at your fingertips. Whether it’s an early tipoff or a primetime matchup, we remove the guesswork so you can bet smarter—night after night, from the regular season to the playoffs and the 2026 NBA Finals. NBA predictions for this week’s games Dimers’ NBA predi",
      "date": "2026-05-17 07:42:09"
    },
    {
      "title": "NBA西部决赛马刺强碰雷霆深度分析来了!看好马刺4:2掀翻卫冕军",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_0516a08f1b053352",
      "snippet": "<p>卫冕冠军雷霆,终于迎来了自己最忌惮的对手｡马刺于北京时间16日以139:109大胜森林狼,系列赛4:2顺利淘汰对手,时隔九年重返NBA西部决赛,接下来将直接挑战卫冕强队雷霆｡马刺和雷霆的西决较量,四大关键看点直接决定系列赛走向:</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.",
      "date": "2026-05-17 06:37:36"
    },
    {
      "title": "The Best Player For Every NBA Franchise",
      "link": "https://www.imdb.com/list/ls525024951/",
