{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{
  "organic": [
    {
      "title": "小勒布朗·詹姆斯",
      "link": "https://baike.baidu.com/item/小勒布朗·詹姆斯/22852865",
      "snippet": "\"小勒布朗·詹姆斯(LeBron James Jr.)是NBA球星勒布朗·詹姆斯的大儿子｡",
      "date": "2026-05-17 07:52:54"
    },
    {
      "title": "詹姆斯谈与杰伦·布朗关系:尊重为主,夏季联赛争议除外",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_553699f34a990452",
      "snippet": "<p>勒布朗谈与杰伦·布朗关系:彼此尊重,唯一分歧在夏季联赛</p><p>今夜达成43000分里程碑,喜悦与悲情并存</p><p>詹姆斯</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-2194418549-871C0E93C3936908245B4491EB6264A7/0?",
      "date": "2026-02-26 01:44:56"
    },
    {
      "title": "詹姆斯父子同场竞技,布朗尼连拿5分,父子情深共谱篮球佳话",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_72069f001f672152",
      "snippet": "<p>父子情深,同场竞技,詹姆斯巧助布朗尼空中接力,演技助攻,一球得分,共创辉煌</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-4225585137-7D018BC0093889B212D2BBDCE03A87B4/0?fmt=jpg&size=122&h=252&w=498&ppv=1' ",
      "date": "2026-04-28 08:42:28"
    },
    {
      "title": "詹姆斯标志性动作诠释职业生涯,20年前元素预示未来成就",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_0516999f95a93752",
      "snippet": "<p>老詹标志性动作源自高中,勾子品牌皇冠logo彰显其王者风范</p><p>从全明星带头大哥到稳坐历史第二把交椅,他成功预判了职业生涯</p><p>詹姆斯</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-875259926-40024D7842C6FB3F96E53DE03F2CB6A7/0?",
      "date": "2026-02-22 02:31:11"
    },
    {
      "title": "詹姆斯又要做救世主?美篮球自媒体lakeshowcp晒图写道:历史似乎又开始低语",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_58269ff3b8c56152",
      "snippet": "<p>詹姆斯,救世主再现?历史低语逆转,他掌控局面</p><p>2016年总决赛,2019年西决,2020夺冠,今季再创奇迹?篮球</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-3824755493-08D2714BE2AF344D8740E53A40C9CC98/0?",
      "date": "2026-05-09 21:50:27"
    },
    {
      "title": "Decision One: The Controversial Focus That LeBron James Cannot Fully Clear_the_During_and",
      "link": "https://www.sohu.com/a/885330283_122328931",
      "snippet": "On July 8, 2010, LeBron James made a pivotal announcement that changed the landscape of the NBA forever. During a televised special called 'The Decision,' he declared that he would leave the Cleveland Cavaliers to join the Miami Heat, forming a monumental trio with Dwyane Wade and Chris Bosh. While this decision led to significant success for James, winning multiple championships, it has also left an indelible mark of controversy in his career. The Backlash: A Departure from Loyalty '\"Decision One\" is a highly contentious episode in sports history, marked by feelings of betrayal from Cleveland fans. By announcing his departure on national television, James not only shocked the Cavaliers organization but also humiliated the city of Cleveland. Cavaliers owner Dan Gilbert's vehement response intensified the conflict, labeling James’ exit as a 'selfish betrayal.' This event forced fans to grapple with a new interpretation of the player-team loyalty dynamics in the NBA. Historical Context :",
      "date": "2025-04-17 01:03:00"
    },
    {
      "title": "突发!老詹亲穿「LeBron 23」!又回到 “那个风格” 了!",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_07668899cef10752",
      "snippet": "<p>又到了每年这个时候,最新一代 Nike LeBron 23 战靴终于揭开神秘面纱!</p><p>今年依旧由詹姆斯训练亲穿曝光,尽管在他自己的 Ins 上打了码,但清晰图片已经流出｡</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-1247445871-D6CAFCA54F15D3617C56FDD2C78D3B87/0?",
      "date": "2025-07-30 12:17:51"
